description:
Kitchen Basics, an American original, inspired by homemade. Everyone knows the deep, concentrated flavor of a perfect homemade stock. It's rich. It's savory. And Kitchen Basics rivals that authentic, premium taste. We craft our mouthwatering liquid gold by simmering the finest quality McCormick Gourmet herbs and spices with chicken and vegetables to extract layers of hearty flavor. The result - a dark, high-quality stock that inspires quick, flavorful dinners and company-worthy feasts alike. The Heart-Healthy Choice for Ingredient-Conscious Cooks: Our stock is a key ingredient for your best culinary creations-soups, sauces, pastas, marinades, vegetables. Use Kitchen Basics stock instead of broth in your favorite recipes-for a great way to add more flavor without as much sodium.

Directions:
Shake before use. Kitchen Basics is an all natural product and may have naturally occurring protein deposits. These are normal and can be dissipated by heating. Refrigerate unused portion. Good for 7 days. Ready to use. Do not dilute. Refrigerate after opening and use within 7 days. Freeze leftover stock in freezable container or ice cube trays. Store frozen stock cubes in a resealable plastic bag and use within 60 days. Recommended use by date on package.
title: Kitchen Basics Stock Chicken 32 oz

bullets: No artificial ingredients

Heart healthy

description: To make dishes more flavorful The Secret is Swanson®. Whatever you're cooking, Swanson® broth, stock, Swanson® Flavor Boost® or Flavor Infused Broth can make your dish more flavorful. Broth Swanson® broths are ideal for use in all your favorite recipes. Whether chicken, beef or vegetable, its a delicious, 100% natural and fat free way to add taste to many meal ideas. Made with high quality farm-grown vegetables and a pinch of sea salt, these full-bodied stocks offer robust flavor and will keep your dishes juicy and enhance their natural flavors.Flavor Boost® Elevate your everyday dishes instantly with Swanson® Flavor Boost® concentrated broth, a kitchen essential that adds flavor to any recipe. Add exciting flavor and variety to your meal repertoire without the hassle of hard to find ingredients. * Small amount of glutamate occurs naturally in yeast extract.
